{"tid":1367901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張建宗︰政府一直思考如何解決困局","createTime":"2019-07-26T11:20:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T11:40:50.000Z","uid":20933,"like":4,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b2ec184fc72acd9d943305c974dcd6020613dff7","tid":1367901,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:20:29.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】周日元朗襲擊事件，受傷入院的45人中仍有四人留醫，政務司司長張建宗承認警方當日的處理手法與市民期望有落差致歉，他同時呼籲明天前往元朗的市民要以和平理性的方式表達訴求。<br />\n<br />\n網民發起周六再到元朗抗議，政務司司長張建宗見記者指明白市民想以行動表達不滿，但呼籲要保持和平理性，不要衝擊當區居民及設施。他又再提起周日元朗西鐵站的襲擊事件，形容施襲者是「暴徒」又承認警方處理手法與市民期望有落差，願意為此向市民致歉。<br />\n<br />\n至於為何不成立獨立調查委員會，張建宗重申由監警會處理會較合適，對於如何解決當前困局，張建宗表示政府一直在思考。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗呼籲市民不要濫用999以免影響需要協助的人。而民政事務局局長劉江華表示，整個元朗無論是商戶或市民都感到擔心，當局會繼續呼籲各方保持和平理性表達訴求。"},{"pid":"68000e3dda521e955018cdfe1f171983db05bafc","tid":1367901,"uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:20:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sIdUzN8MMK8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsIdUzN8MMK8&d=d2KrXihf468bG0awDawljpKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=551eedcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sIdUzN8MMK8</a>"},{"pid":"6aac68d4cdb4a37fed30147a76d80f5ca039590b","tid":1367901,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:20:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=356882\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D356882&d=d2KrXihf468bG0awDawljpKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=f09ebb2a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D356882&h=c1dc3d93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=356882</a>"},{"pid":"38b3335037581676b0da4c9d5ccb51aa46ab5458","tid":1367901,"uid":3775,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:21:31.000Z","msg":"拎返i